{"tid":2397753,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國放水第二集","createTime":"2021-02-06T16:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T18:22:58.000Z","uid":391458,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"354bf4f0f02fe2d76e4b8fead5451ddd02c77616","tid":2397753,"uid":391458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"QE alone, and QE plus fiscal spending, are two very different things when it comes to affecting broad money supply.<br />\n<br />\nLyn Alden 2/6/21<br />\n<br />\n美國史無前例咁樣放第二輪水，你哋自己估吓Bitcoin, Ethereum 會升到上去乜嘢位？用膝頭哥都諗到啦！<br />\n<br />\n你覺得一年內美國可以收水咩？ 我教你啦，乜嘢都係睇水流。到佢話唔再放水或者收水嗰陣時，Bitcoin, Ethereum 仲喺度狂升，啲人喺度又話乜嘢大時代又話經濟完全回復，嗰陣時先係最伏，先係最後瘋狂。聽就聽唔聽就撚就！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KFzcJS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KFzcJS.png&h=83fe12e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e19384c94b9f219244e5e3fc5fb408f3f41c46a","tid":2397753,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:44:10.000Z","msg":"gchi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a42a2fcdf7ad449ed8945b302184aa43577799","tid":2397753,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d85eea443715fa3a1161c81aa181aade68f741","tid":2397753,"uid":32782,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:47:00.000Z","msg":"QE親都無可能一年收水 最多停水<br />\n經濟週期起碼要幾年之後先可以開始慢慢收水<br />\n如果唔係冧得仲大獲"},{"pid":"2668ce93488a13a832520e92672c8cb39039524e","tid":2397753,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:47:32.000Z","msg":"24年先加息"},{"pid":"28374e205ed4cb1df0315dd89cbc127a7866ec70","tid":2397753,"uid":99125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T16:49:11.000Z","msg":"賺錢咁易就好囉<br />\n今年個財長係Yellen，同埋最近嘅經濟數據都顯示通脹升溫"},{"pid":"b0a87ef306b2a632b56664dfa44a90c962cc1ef1"