都唔太信網上資訊"},{"pid":"c06e86d3387b072c0e41e81f11ff1c59370300db","tid":2397753,"uid":391458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77c4e54c02dfbc759b9d5bb92e186d9758a162a4","tid":2397753,"uid":102081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:57:37.000Z","msg":"好難講，經過gme事件後，好多人都唔太信網上資訊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:11:11.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單，每次放水就升。收水，唔放水就跌或者放唔夠水。2008，2015，2018，2020 每一次都係咁。咁咪睇吓今次去瘋狂印銀紙，將2020年之前嘅所有美元佢一年之內印多5成夠唔夠囉。今次印得特別誇張因為大部份嘅錢去咗Stimulus，呢個係broad money。世界歷史上每一次broad money直升，都係勁通貨膨脹。我睇油價繼續上升添⋯⋯😳😳😳<br />\n<br />\nQE alone, and QE plus fiscal spending, are two very different things when it comes to affecting broad money supply.<br />\n<br />\nFolks often wonder why Japan didn't have inflation over the past 20 years despite their central bank balance sheet going vertical.<br />\n<br />\nIt's because their broad money supply grew very slowly.<br />\n<br />\nBase money going vertical, and broad money going vertical, are two very different things.<br />\n<br />\n- Lyn Alden 2/4/21<br />\n<br />\nVery important distinction<br />\n<br />\nInteresting to note broad USD starting to head vertical in this chart<br />\n<br />\n- Joseph Brown 2/4/21<br />\n<br />\nLyn Alden 2/6/21<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDjoUje.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDjoUje.png&h=1e1c0580&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7215752837e290d936acffe36577119fca170b3e","tid":2397753,"uid":391458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77c4e54c02dfbc759b9d5bb92e186d9758a162a4","tid":2397753,"uid":102081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:57:37.000Z","msg":"好難講，經過gme事件後，好多人都唔太信網上資訊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:41:42.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單，每次放水就升。收水，唔放水或者放唔夠水就會跌。2008，2015，2018，2020 每一次都係咁。咁咪睇吓今次去瘋狂印銀紙，將2020年之前嘅所有美元佢一年之內印多5成夠唔夠囉。今次印得特別誇張因為大部份嘅錢去咗Stimulus，呢個係broad money。世界歷史上每一次broad money直升，都係勁通貨膨脹。我睇油價繼續上升添⋯⋯😳😳😳<br />\n<br />\nQE alone, and QE plus fiscal spending, are two very different things when it comes to affecting broad money supply.<br />\n<br />\nFolks often wonder why Japan didn't have inflation over the past 20 years despite their central bank balance sheet going vertical.<br />\n<br />\nIt's because their broad money supply grew very slowly.<br />\n<br />\nBase money going vertical, and broad money going vertical, are two very different things.<br />\n<br />\n- Lyn Alden 2/4/21<br />\n<br />\nVery important distinction<br />\n<br />\nInteresting to note broad USD starting to head vertical in this chart<br />\n<br />\n- Joseph Brown 2/4/21<br />\n<br />\nLyn Alden 2/6/21<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJzwjgR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJzwjgR.png&h=01bbbc73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99f1ca77b9f20b6f00df5dfb1391da2f418abeed","tid":2397753,"uid":81757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78b33dc0644f9140907cd41c2a5a802923f2292d","tid":2397753,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26462dc605a5e9a139c3eda81913062308e8759e","tid":2397753,"uid":81757,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"美國肯定滯脹，如無意外今年發生<br />\n滯脹下 陷入 唔放死 放又死<br />\n到時慘過大肅條<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:19:49.000Z","msg":"造夠百鳩幾枚金幣搞撚掂哂，輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"如果咁簡單就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a2116bab35ea0e985326447e3910ef8c1bf204","tid":2397753,"uid":81757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1731198a77b82365098afbd48fe15fd6d7c723b1","tid":2397753,"uid":100045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13aab26a56a172a7e8975cc4f64e98d22c3dd0f7","tid":2397753,"uid":102081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy